---
import Layout from "../layouts/Global.astro";

// Pre-render this page at build time
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="MCP Server Demo">
  <div class="mcp-demo">
    <h1>MCP Server Demo</h1>
    
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Available MCP Tools</h2>
      <p>The Serendie MCP server provides the following tools:</p>
      
      <div class="tool">
        <h3>1. health-check</h3>
        <p>Check if the MCP server is running properly.</p>
        <pre>No input required</pre>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool">
        <h3>2. get-design-tokens</h3>
        <p>Retrieve design tokens for Serendie Design System.</p>
        <pre>{`{
  "theme": "asagi" | "konjo" | "kurikawa" | "sumire" | "tsutsuji",
  "category": "color" | "spacing" | "typography" | "all"
}`}</pre>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool">
        <h3>3. get-component-info</h3>
        <p>Get detailed information about UI components.</p>
        <pre>{`{
  "componentName": "button" // optional, returns all if not specified
}`}</pre>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool">
        <h3>4. search-documentation</h3>
        <p>Search through Serendie documentation.</p>
        <pre>{`{
  "query": "your search query",
  "category": "components" | "pages" | "all",
  "limit": 10
}`}</pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>MCP Endpoint</h2>
      <p>The MCP server is available at:</p>
      <code class="endpoint">/api/mcp</code>
      <p>This endpoint supports the Model Context Protocol for AI assistants to interact with the Serendie Design System.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Integration</h2>
      <p>To use this MCP server with an AI assistant that supports the Model Context Protocol:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Configure your AI assistant to connect to the MCP endpoint</li>
        <li>The assistant will have access to all the tools listed above</li>
        <li>It can retrieve design tokens, component information, and search documentation</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .mcp-demo {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--colors-sd-system-color-text-primary);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--colors-sd-system-color-text-primary);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--colors-sd-system-color-text-secondary);
  }

  .tool {
    background-color: var(--colors-sd-system-component-surfaceDim);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tool p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  pre {
    background-color: var(--colors-sd-system-component-surface);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--colors-sd-system-color-border-primary);
  }

  code.endpoint {
    background-color: var(--colors-sd-system-component-surfaceDim);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  ol {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>